### Security Rules
- All API keys via environment variables — never hardcoded
- Version numbers are internal only — client-facing docs use "updated proposal"
- Each client document needs its own separate Dropbox share link

### Active Projects
Active projects are tracked in the symphonysh repo at `src/data/projects.ts`. Do NOT hardcode project names or financial details here — they change frequently.

### Prompts Directory
All task prompts are in `.cursor/prompts/`. Key prompts: A–N (infrastructure/trading), Q (full audit), S (Cortex merge), T (approval drain), U (DB consolidation), V (CLAUDE.md accuracy). The DONE/ subfolder contains completed prompts.
